snippet.title: Test of Insanity - Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Second trailer for the game "The Test of Insanity", showing how insane people get when playing it.

---------------------------------
Wishlist on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3083960/The_Test_of_Insanity

Demo playable on Itch.io:
https://bignutsgames.itch.io/the-test-of-insanity

Demo Frontpaged (Daily top 3 and Underdog of the week) on Newgrounds:
https://www.newgrounds.com/portal/view/938341

The footage is from a French movie called "Les Sous-Doués (1980)".
https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0081541/

The music is from the game itself.
